{"tid":595951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[CLS] IU黑粉「一刀切斷她脖子」　驚悚畫面曝光！","createTime":"2018-03-17T07:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T07:57:43.000Z","uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d085a5c22417534ce6e2f7957032564eee3afc31","tid":595951,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"南韓女歌手IU（아이유，本名李知恩이지은）以甜美外型和音樂實力備受喜愛， 每每發行新歌都橫掃排行榜，因此有「音源強盜」的稱號，人氣可見一斑。但她卻疑似遭到黑粉在網路上攻擊，驚悚畫面讓不少粉絲都怒指：「看了很不舒服！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3169/d3169193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3169%2Fd3169193.jpg&h=b7a8c263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU《YOU&amp;I 》時期的黑洋裝、雙馬尾造型。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在推特上傳疑似慶生的影片，蛋糕上是IU《YOU&amp;I 》時期的黑洋裝、雙馬尾造型。然而影片中卻出現「一刀從脖子劃下」、「把臉切分成四半」的畫面。此舉讓許多粉絲不滿，紛紛湧入該推特，指責道：「就算不喜歡也不需要如此吧，這已經是死亡威脅了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3169/d3169180.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3169%2Fd3169180.gif&h=478e508b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3169/d3169188.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3169%2Fd3169188.gif&h=946b4b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU造型的蛋糕被粉絲一刀從脖子切下，臉也被劃成四半。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n雖然該網友已經刪除影片，並在推特表示：「我很抱歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">忽略了對蛋糕上圖案的行為會造成種人反感。</span>」但截圖依然瘋傳，粉絲也希望公司能視為警訊，更加注意IU的人身安全和反擊黑粉的變態行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3169/d3169192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3169%2Fd3169192.jpg&h=7b02c2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU造型的蛋糕在推特引起軒然大波。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"ebb4a9846e44087794ce18394fdd6fb5fcf5ac51","tid":595951,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"紅字真係搵鬼信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9df2da3b61859f7e70080a5edb4adba269f85e","tid":595951,"uid":170134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"生日蛋糕黎？<br />\n愛佢愛到生日蛋糕都整iu黎慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3b3773cd07223bf281113234bc1bbd0cd0ca56","tid":595951,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"條片既震幅同把刀係同步, 推翻拍片係同一個人所為, 而且冇杯碟, 不存在多人慶祝生日既耍樂方式<br />\n<br />\n影片再上傳到網絡上, 推斷極有可能係惡意行為, 等收信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0444b55ecbbb5987dc11d1088eb68c9fb75fa51b","tid":595951,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"}]}